    "body": "thanks,@zcbenz: i success use the Pointer Lock API to lock the mouse!\n\nit requires focus to the browser window.\n\nits cool!\n\n``` javascript\nvar canvas = document.getElementById(\"game\");\ncanvas.requestPointerLock(); //focus the window first or the request would be failed\n```\n\n![default](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6326007/8932151/bf63f968-356d-11e5-89ee-ed4d3accee29.PNG)\n\n### more info about Pointer Lock API\n\nhttps://www.chromium.org/developers/design-documents/mouse-lock\nhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Pointer_Lock_API\nhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/requestPointerLock\nhttp://www.w3.org/TR/pointerlock/\n"
